Package: pcdid
Type: Package
Title: Principal Components Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-07-12
Authors@R: c(person("Xiaolei", "Wang", , "adamwang15@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-6192-9061")), person("Marc", "Chan", , "marc.chan@unimelb.edu.au", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1010-7587")))
Maintainer: Xiaolei Wang <adamwang15@gmail.com>
Description: Implements the Principal Components Difference-in-Differences (PCDID) estimator in Chan, M. K., & Kwok, S. S. (2022) <doi:10.1080/07350015.2021.1914636>. PCDID uses factor proxies constructed from control units to control for unobserved trends, assuming that the unobservables follow an interactive effects structure.
